text: Kugarchi () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kugarchinsky Selsoviet, Kugarchinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 787 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 34 km from Mrakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kugarchinsky District
title: Kugarchi, Kugarchinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
